summary: SummaryHighlightsCruelty Freee.l.f.'s Incredi-Curl Mascara is a buildable, volumizing and curling mascara that grips lashes for big, bold curl and volume that lasts. The curved, dense bristle brush catches each lash to volumize, lift and set curl for an eye-opening effect. The formula is smudge, flake, and transfer-resistant.
details: DetailsBenefitsBuildable formula grips each lash for lasting curl & extreme volumeCurved, double-sided bristle brush volumizes, lifts & sets curlsSmudge, flake & transfer-resistant formulae.l.f. is double-certified cruelty-free by Leaping Bunny & PETAe.l.f. is proud to partner with Fair Trade USA & manufacture products in Fair Trade Certified facilities; look for the Fair Trade Certified seal on your e.l.f. productResearch Results102% improvement in curl*88% saw bigger & bolder lashes***In an instrumental test**In a consumer perception testFormulated WithoutPhthalatesParabensNonylphenol ethoxylatesTriclosanTriclocarbanHydroquinoneItem 2639452How To UseBefore applying curl mascara, gently wipe excess product off the tip of the wand.Align the inner curve of the wand at the base of your lashes and wiggle mascara wand upwards in a zig-zag motion to coat lashes from root to tip.Use the outer curve of the wand to layer additional coats to curl all the way up and turn on volume.IngredientsBrown: Water (Aqua), Styrene/Acrylates Copolymer, Propylene Glycol, Synthetic Beeswax, Ricinus Communis (Castor) Seed Oil, Copernicia Cerifera (Carnauba) Wax, Glyceryl Stearate, PVP, Polyamide-5, Polyacrylic Acid, Palmitic Acid, PEG-8 Caprylic/Capric Glycerides, Hydrogenated Polyisobutene, Nylon-12, PEG-100 Stearate, Acrylates Copolymer, Magnesium Aluminum Silicate, Stearic Acid, Phenoxyethanol, PEG-40 Hydrogenated Castor Oil, Aminomethyl Propanol, Ethylhexylglycerin, Polyquaternium-10, PEG-90M, Crambe Abyssinica Seed Oil, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil, Alcohol, Sodium Benzoate, Silica, Tocopherol. May Contain: Iron Oxides (CI 77499, CI 77491, CI 77492), Titanium Dioxide (CI 77891).Ingredients may change or vary from time to time. Please refer to the packaging of the product you receive for the list of ingredients in your particular product.
how_to_use: Before applying curl mascara, gently wipe excess product off the tip of the wand.Align the inner curve of the wand at the base of your lashes and wiggle mascara wand upwards in a zig-zag motion to coat lashes from root to tip.Use the outer curve of the wand to layer additional coats to curl all the way up and turn on volume.

reviews.headline: Great mascara, perfect for a young adult!
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] This mascara is really good. I love how high quality it is. It helps lengthen my lashes without making them look bulky. It provides curls and volume, both which I look for in a mascara. It's water resistant which is another plus. Highly recommend!

reviews.headline: love
reviews.comments: i love the volume this product gives. it's water resistance, had no transfer on my face. no clumpy lashes.  and it made my real lashes look so much longer and fuller

reviews.headline: Noticeable lift
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] The e.l.f. IncrediCurl Mascara in Dark Brown gives lashes a noticeable lift and curl without clumping. Its creamy formula coats each lash evenly, providing definition and a natural-looking volume. The dark brown shade is perfect for a softer, everyday look while still enhancing your eyes, and the brush design makes application quick and precise. Long-lasting and smudge-resistant, it's a great option for a polished, effortless lash look.

reviews.headline: Dramatic + Defined
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] This mascara delivers a bold black finish that really makes the lashes pop. The formula glides on easily and gives a dramatic look in just a couple of swipes. It's perfect for those who love a dark, defined lash.

reviews.headline: I like it
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] My lashes are already long but I did see a difference when I put it on. It doesnt feel heavy like other ones. I also don't use an eyelash curler, if I did, it would've give it more volume. This might be my next new mascara. ☺️

reviews.headline: Pretty
reviews.comments:
[I received this product in exchange for my honest review] Very pretty mascara. Keeps lashes separated and beautiful. My eyelashes have a really hard time staying curled so they do end up straight
 after use but I don't think most people would have that issue

reviews.headline: Good Mascara, a Little Messy
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] I thought this mascara worked well and was long lasting. My main issue with it is that it's kind of messy, so you gotta be careful. I thought it did help with curl like it said. Easy to apply. Doesn't clump.

reviews.headline: Fine mascara, wouldn't give up your go-to
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] Mascara was decidedly fine, very gloopy especially when taking the wand out of the tube. Gave a nice natural look to my lashes, photos show before & immediately after, no curler was used before applying. Longevity was on par with other mascaras I've tried before, although there was some flaking by the time I was done with my work day.

reviews.headline: I like this mascara
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] My eyelashes don't curl but this helps them curl. Ingredients are on the better side. I appreciate the brush and way it applies to lashes.  I have super sensitive eyes due to allergies and this doesn't bother me like others.

reviews.headline: Great product
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] Absolutely loved this mascara, it worked so well on my little lashes and elongated them well. It did not clump or ruin my lashes and stayed on all day!

reviews.headline: Definitely recommend
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] I'm not usually a mascara person since my lashes are super straight. However, after curling and using this mascara it gave my straight lashes some curls. Removing it was easy. Definitely will use again.

reviews.headline: Long beautiful lashes!
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] This mascara is awesome! I absolutely adore a high quality affordable mascara and this is it to a T! Makes your lashes look long and full without clumping together!

reviews.headline: My favorite
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] This is a beautiful mascara. The applicator is large but great for enhancing the natural curl of the lash. This is the dark brown color and looks natural.

reviews.headline: Love
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] I tried the Mascara and it does a nice job making my lashes look curled and open. It goes on smooth, no heavy clumps, and feels light. It's not too bold, but great for an everyday natural look. Easy to remove at night too, which I really like. Highly recommended!!

reviews.headline: Such a great mascara
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] Gives my lashes amazing curl and volume that lasts all day without clumping. Easy to apply, comfortable to wear, and removes effortlessly!!!!

reviews.headline: Good!
reviews.comments: The product is decent and it's not clumpy

reviews.headline: Great mascara!
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] Lengthens my lashes super well and washes off relatively easily (though it's relatively smudge proof). Curls/volume lasted all day and the curved spoolie makes it really easy to apply to my lashes. Ingredients seem to be decent, especially considering the price! Definitely recommend.

reviews.headline: Good for natural separation
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] So this is pretty good if you want to start out your mascara routine. It helps define the way you would like your lashes formed with little clumping. However if you apply many coats like you do with other mascaras it offers no build on length so I would not use this as an everyday wear. It is easy to remove though so that's a bonus!

reviews.headline: Great mascara
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] I think elf makes a really good mascara, and this one did not disappoint me at all. I love that it was brown and looked really natural with my make up instead of using a harsh black color. This retained my curls very well and kept my mascara on all night long. It was very easy to apply

reviews.headline: Great Product for the Price
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] I only use waterproof madcaras because I have asian eyelashes, and normally also stick to asian beauty brands. However, this mascara does a great job of holding my eyelashes up and curled throughout the day. I like that this formula is on the drier side because if the formula is too wet my lashes fall faster. I got good separation between lashes and between coats.

faceoff_positive.comments: I didn't have high expectations for this mascara going in, although there are several Elf products I do like (I'm a high end makeup girly). I was very impressed by this mascara! The coloring is great, it lasted all day and it did very well doing several coats- it was super buildable and made my eyes pop! I would definitely purchase this and save my coins!
faceoff_positive.headline: Great bang for your buck!

faceoff_negative.comments: I got the product the product for free from elf in exchange for a review. It's okay, not amazing. The curl is definitely there right after applying, and the shade is super black, which I liked. It makes your lashes pop without looking too heavy. But after a few hours, I noticed the curl started to fall, and it didn't hold up well throughout the day especially if you have straight lashes like mine. It's not clumpy, but it doesn't give a ton of volume either, so if you're going for a really bold lash look, this might not be it. The wand is kind of awkward at first but gets better once you get used to it. I'd say it's a decent everyday mascara, just not something I'd rave about.
